Simplecert module for Moodle - version 2.0
==========================================

Created by Shane Elliott, Pukunui

Description:
    Create a certificate using a background image and text entered via GUI

Installation:
    * see http://docs.moodle.org/en/Installing_contributed_modules_or_plugins


